<Privacy>:
    size_hint_y: None
    height: '300dp'
    orientation: 'vertical'
    # spacing: "10dp"
    
    MDLabel:
        text: "Privacy Policy"
        bold: True
        font_size: '25dp'
        size_hint_y: None
        adaptive_height: True
    ScrollView:
        MDBoxLayout:
            size_hint_y: None
            adaptive_height: True
            orientation: 'vertical'
            spacing: "30dp"
            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                text: 'Make sure to read this carefully before continuing.'

            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                color: 'gray'
                text: 'This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use and protect personal information from users. We are dedicated to protecting the personal information we collect from you. By using our platform you consent to the practices described in this privacy policy.'

            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                color: 'gray'
                markup: True
                text: '[b][color=#000000]User Account Creation[/color][/b] \n1. When you create an account, we collect your personal information such as your email. This information is necessary to connect advertisers to their buyers and vice versa to facilitate communication and for security purposes.'

            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                color: 'gray'
                markup: True
                text: '2. We use personal information you provide to contact you and send you notifications or messages regarding your advertised or requested properties, and verifying your identity. We may use this information to conduct data analysis, monitor usage patterns and enhance overall user satisfaction.'

            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                color: 'gray'
                markup: True
                text: '[b][color=#000000]Advertising Properties[/color][/b] \n1. Before you successfully publish your property, we collect information such as your account email and phonenumber. Other options are provided such as social media from messanger, twitter and whatsapp to provide comfort on the method of communication between you and your buyer.'

            MDLabel:
                size_hint_y: None
                adaptive_height: True
                color: 'gray'
                markup: True
                text: "2. Before you successfully publish your property, we collect detailed infromation about such as location, number of bedrooms, bathrooms, property type and the price you're advertising for. The information we collect is to provide total transparency to viewers who might be interested in your property."


